
 * Voices have been generated using : 
- festival (http://www.cstr.ed.ac.uk/projects/festival) 
- US1 MBROLA voice (http://www.cstr.ed.ac.uk/projects/festival/mbrola.html)

 * ~/.festivalrc
(Parameter.set 'Audio_Method 'linux16audio)
;; (set! voice_default 'voice_rab_diphone)
;; (set! voice_default 'voice_don_diphone)
(set! voice_default 'voice_us1_mbrola)

 * Command line : text2wave file.txt -o output.wav
(from the Festival toolbox)

 * Using Audacity to correct sounds :
-> bitrate = 16bits
-> sample rate = 22k
-> apply Compressor effect with -14dB gain

